\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The next morning they headed out to Castlerock and from there, made the journey to Amelrak. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Robert sat in the X2 at the co-pilot seat alongside Smoke. At the moment, the ship was on autopilot and they were flying over the ocean. It would be hours before they made it to Amelrak. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The fleet of Blue Dragons and rebels, the A1, X1 and X2 were all taking different routes. That way, in the event that the Kwans tried to take them out before reaching the city, they would have to split up their forces to do so.}}